<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Jun1930"><font color="red">1 June 1930</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Helen Fleischmann): He also received the book I asked you to send and is very happy to have it and Mrs Joyce was reading it to him today and he seemed very much interested </div>
